  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 홍보물 제작,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인, 인쇄물 모두</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-fabc0d63-151c-48b5-8aed-7fd4e5195302\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/001.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">차량이나 철문에 붙이는 종이자석</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>종이자석</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2dbae985-744f-45a5-94d7-ffbbcab4e987\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 품목은 차량이나 철문에 붙여서 홍보할 수 있는 스티커의 하나입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8c6ee65b-8306-4e58-8737-ff2dd9cbddab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-40f6eb38-d022-42e4-8279-ac772add50f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9061ce68-5e3c-4629-a354-deddbbb4cbca\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d39314a4-2e78-4309-8b76-be16335e164d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후면에 자석이 부착되어 철문이나 차량 문에 강력하게 붙여서 사용할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-00a84c02-9408-49d7-871e-b3e20ae2aaad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c76ca39-9007-43a1-bbb1-4781c2db576a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">차량용 스티커이니 만큼 자석의 부착력은 강력한 편입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3dcf17c0-cc22-4b3d-acc9-f87aa63ba22c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-27ace6f9-d455-46c9-9a39-0a02f74cad9b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7bca4a47-f830-40d7-bd8e-2898a1d7d731\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b4ff4987-0f46-46d0-8ea4-84ae5d2127be\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사양은 다음과 같습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93f435ed-ae03-4fb8-a099-8dbd8276862a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4164891f-f335-4a0e-a57d-e52580eee3d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75ee6af6-cf07-470d-8a32-79c4a67654df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-91bf6b11-5636-42b6-9225-61f0f1b01473\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-427a0aff-43da-4576-959c-10b46da79773\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 자유롭게 제작이 가능합니다. 기본은 수십 미터에서 5cm까지 다양합니다. 다만 최소 사이즈는 50mm 즉 5cm입니다. 그 이상이 돼야 재단이 됩니다. 그 이하를 원하시면 톰슨(도무송)으로 따야 하고 비용이 많이 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47b9caff-51e8-414b-8f3f-ce7fb00afd6c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9e49c5e3-d56a-4ff4-b6c9-b59d720d25c0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-387190df-6c51-464d-99ee-063218965996\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7742588a-8565-4b7e-a41f-fa842e273477\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>용지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-57bbf493-37b6-4461-a98f-5ad6a76ea408\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 유포지 + 자석 합지입니다. 자석 합지에 유포지를 붙여서 제작하는 형태입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6bca45aa-5744-411d-aedc-bdae16e67b66\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-85c1fe67-86b7-489f-b8a2-0c07728be0c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac658179-0ee6-450c-bd16-ac67ac5c8d65\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4dc5058e-ab83-4817-ade7-b3c3944bd766\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>잉크</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b98d1e1-ec9c-40ba-a6f4-2f3692dab910\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 수성잉크를 사용합니다. 수성잉크는 물에 약하고 공기 중에 노출이 되면 쉽게 변색이 되고 잉크가 마릅니다. 이를 방지하기 위해 반드시 코팅 작업이 이루어져야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cb844d9-18be-4774-a272-1a83e084fdc8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0e5e42f-c49c-401a-83b2-f966cdec9108\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-68e30771-8f2f-4ea9-b8a1-a0537559f50c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d30dd0a2-296c-4c2f-be80-28b12255ea54\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d26572f5-4315-413a-9db0-768e89c2f41b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 인쇄는 단면만 제작이 가능하며 별색이나 다른 색의 작업을 불가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c92da96-bad4-4eb7-a913-30b72c5af8ef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-445ad8d8-0a7b-420d-acec-ab1f1907b633\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1cf8ca92-a738-4bbc-a8b1-85f2aa5b3de7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70de39d8-ce6a-4076-a632-9091753505f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29db103d-1571-439e-babb-388af9a90471\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 코팅을 해야 오래 변색 없이 버틸 수 있습니다. 코팅이 없이 작업은 불가능합니다. 간혹 코팅 없이 친환경을 요구하시는 분이 계십니다. 그러면 제품으로서의 역할이나 수명이 짧기에 추천드리지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1eaec56-5e2c-4947-bb64-c0af219bf720\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a3d1c113-403e-42c1-9d29-591f65b72a4f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">코팅은 무광/유광 중에 선택할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0b1b1a0-3c6e-438f-ae8b-cdd0a96740a2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15a0e049-4e13-4d31-aceb-fcb4e89b2063\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-94809459-1df5-4d3f-9d03-cca2620c1f97\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c010b8be-daec-4fcc-ad0a-24bd23d1aadc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-52fd869f-2755-4eba-98ea-77c6f5e549f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 사각 재단으로 할 수 있고 모양 도무송(톰슨)으로 처리도 가능합니다. 도무송작업시 비용이 비싸지만 자유롭게 모양을 만들어 사용해 보시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-274ff422-dd8f-4fdd-a4dc-26c2e7273082\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-952b118c-6241-4375-be93-fc8ebd77723b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6f01749-739a-47f9-b098-00729ac465bd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2ebb19a1-b67b-479f-9f95-e3c3d8048e5f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04882a5a-33da-4b5e-94c1-a8ae0dcfe5a2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">칼선을 다음과 같이 만들어서 모양으로 차량스티커를 만드셔도 좋을 겁니다. 다만 모양이 너무 복작하지 않게 작업하는 것이 중요합니다. 위 모양도 복잡하여 단순화하는 것이 작업에 도움이 되며 오히려 깔끔하게 제작이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65d60983-629d-4a26-a06d-d4375ed3aca8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f8a81407-7e2f-499f-9c9a-0cfaed6eae6e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad667531-63e9-4b9b-a278-12e4607b933e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-44e76bd9-c18a-4267-9130-fa3e198c109c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-2fbe7001-3b21-4f4c-bcac-2e3cbfc576e9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbd01264-466b-4885-9941-4b724b73f5e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a65e418f-0488-4e82-ab26-54be9592ceaf\" style=\"\">유리문에 붙이는 포맥스 큐방</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96350682-d6fb-4aa1-91b8-ac3c0f6a799c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5effb8d-32fd-4a95-9196-094aa53a560e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f88c400f-08f1-4248-a9e3-b39a6ac3b376\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>포맥스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58c79810-c283-4494-9f04-cabd74acd801\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 품목은 외부 유리에 붙이는 재질입니다. 차량이나 철문에 붙여서 홍보할 수 있는 스티커의 하나입니다. 폼 보드와 포맥스를 혼동하는 분을 위해 간단히 설명드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2631b59a-e617-4323-8223-2b4ecea6387c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8d9a41b-f6c3-4da4-a7e2-5fc1701fda08\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-377f12d8-9d79-4b7b-904c-a74f4504c5f1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9492bc43-ce3a-4015-9180-92db2570fc4e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>폼보드</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f70b21d-b558-47f0-ad1d-08c8de6bd033\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8e1125ba-00ba-4d5b-bd23-6be61d623d22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">폼보드는 우드락 양면에 종이를 합지한 보드입니다. 단점으로는 충격에 꺾임이 있을 수 있지만 두께는 더 두껍게 제작이 가능하여 5T/10T로 제작됩니다. 10T는 10mm입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ccc4691f-402a-45ad-8f9b-d7fdebd3ec00\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff54bea1-c6d5-4a0e-8f74-1303ee760b75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd5a5c8a-f10f-4619-90fc-4d14706d6143\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-69286c12-4a86-46e1-85e4-0673aa347f88\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>포맥스</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95bfa710-ed91-4626-af3f-cf492db345b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-579db08e-8370-4df6-8446-cb86c3aec0eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포맥스는 폴리스틸렌을 발포하여 압축한 고밀도 재료입니다. 폼보드보다 내구성이 강하고 웬만해서는 부러지지 않아 외부 거치용으로 사용됩니다. 두께는 3T/5T가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01fa0818-665b-46fd-befd-bcd58bdac7d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-95d50814-71af-4cf2-b38c-0883deded138\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2d7776ce-ff8f-4ff6-8c72-dc5aad3a8475\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-563da6f1-4554-4617-8a82-b841909a5d99\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>두 재료 모두 두껍기 때문에 타공으로 제작이 가능하며 모양으로 딸 수는 있지만 비용이 많이 드는 단점이 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b361ebe-478a-4b6f-8eb3-f17878ec7a7c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/007.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0347ce7f-7dac-4cbb-9515-cfcea556d1d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7fec5bec-a034-4733-9c52-98d57de7ceed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4171ba4f-bd94-460d-81af-40f6d695d5f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지는 포맥스 3T에 타공으로 큐방을 끼워 제작한 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c19a78c-a564-41c3-8b28-8f84beabd2e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a01555b-e5cd-4f7d-bae9-660d81642500\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26cedfb0-5886-4b32-8bbe-a38e161425af\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70a1c7bd-ea20-4e38-9f34-e53b20d089bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>큐방</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35725dd1-6288-43f4-b159-9e55c1cd9ff0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5b52a0a4-08fc-4ccf-a762-34f8885c72ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">큐방은 접착식 압축 재료라고 보시면 됩니다. 유리문에 공기 압축으로 고정시킬 수 있는 부자재입니다. 물론 영구적이지 않고 쉽게 떨어지기도 하지만 가장 합리적으로 유리문 등에 부착할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4001d234-586b-46e0-a193-3778751422c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/008.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37ed12da-bae0-4a2b-978d-06de791cd2e6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfd4cf63-96fd-484d-85ca-923bf8807bc9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00efb7e3-db17-4423-84f6-a0d739a8396b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f4354df-dc1b-4f21-94f7-ce2be79a86b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b38b13f2-82df-4707-8695-8c3067d48b37\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄는 유리 앞뒤 모두 보일 수 있도록 양면 인쇄로 진행했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b978c42a-258d-45ce-86ef-67e0244f223f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223784415941/009.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1b4c734a-a486-46b4-82a8-8dca3b5ceec5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eabbf574-a9d9-49b5-944b-66f7b66379eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-736d8e5b-c65f-40cc-bac5-d44f70e9a27e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사양은 다음과 같습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-80d52c83-9db7-4fb7-9926-fa7274637b85\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8b6e753-79b8-4572-9f1e-c51a7ff56a07\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0e821a1-78a5-4108-8265-066dd9e2735e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-270763dc-1d88-4f7b-ad5e-9de43c72fe78\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c5e7855-3cb1-41ce-906c-c995de7780f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 자유롭게 제작이 가능합니다. 최소 사이즈는 100mm 즉 10cm입니다. 그 이상이 돼야 재단이 됩니다. 그 이하를 원하시면 톰슨(도무송)으로 따야 하고 비용이 많이 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbd5c7f8-bbcd-476f-84f1-765506d895a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-79c886d5-9d05-4461-a92c-e82338a80dea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b11550ea-4af0-4cb7-b2a3-8b256f4f6f4c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c60b45f9-0198-4c46-bc69-3c5c3762459d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>용지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3208cf8d-f917-4894-814d-657a6a57f508\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 유포지 130μ 합지 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-612f0223-1e0c-4b62-bcbe-411e16f9ebfd\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">(포맥스에 바로 인쇄하면 양면인쇄가 불가능합니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd0652f1-09bb-48c2-bca2-0e416a7f935f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08494ac6-699d-420e-ba34-e33bf6f6fd74\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-36a627db-033e-45ba-b616-0a9614d804dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9038632b-ddf1-4b2f-a1a6-371c8e02d409\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>잉크</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-472f5407-a11e-4da9-a54b-100b6ea3831b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 수성잉크</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-969f9ec4-f318-4477-856d-5c1cc27e67da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6177a02a-d5aa-4f11-99fd-2b41a47c6c60\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c196f3c6-38d2-47cf-8dc0-a68c461cecaf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cafeb37d-bf0e-4d72-9a2e-350b8dc79241\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4c991b1-36e5-43b4-9ab5-e911c5774fb8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 인쇄는 양면으로 진행하여 유리 앞뒤로 모두 볼 수 있게 했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5761a9fe-c2cf-43d4-a645-893ce8a560c4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05f99c45-61d6-4ca7-9222-fe1a0c50aad7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ddc5339f-44ab-4dfa-ac23-95bf66e2bd10\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-898565ae-7882-4dc4-9333-a6f7a9799526\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1644a177-0a72-42f1-aa87-71a220563cc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 코팅은 무광/유광 중에 선택할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-199991cf-6d39-4959-babd-d7e12f0cb1a2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cce1453a-83d8-41b1-9511-acddc9be934b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5d93081-a0a0-4217-8a61-858ccb5b07d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-acdba03c-23d0-4bf0-a7fb-b1c87d95f2fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ee236373-f3df-4786-ba92-3e843f21f6fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 큐방자리 타공을 진행했습니다. 사방 4군데 타공으로 제작하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e79d66be-7616-4da0-9744-9508d3b58c92\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38d73fd3-a89c-4e94-8ccf-0721eddeadf8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-3d36c29b-d71e-49cf-aabc-1f0b293411bd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df690f0f-e217-44cf-9750-d665f7431033\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-672d9e52-fb28-4783-9e31-6300aaf9afe7\" style=\"\">이런 곳에 사용하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c77a44fb-c381-4f59-9e32-c31fcc642a48\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5934a38-bf50-427e-8864-99d22add47fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-405f9077-d533-4e2b-8c21-a38ddee3c2f5\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>자석스티커 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d43cf938-37be-41f5-9719-df490bb65ba7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-94ef2499-e7cd-43c8-8a87-ddeeca26d980\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-edc711e4-19fb-4e4c-a9c3-d108f6accb9d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">공사현장 컨테이너 박스의 부착물 용도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-30f731e2-9312-4ee9-9c88-06835a6814ec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14991a20-9ce9-48ca-983b-b0734e103fbc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자주 탈부착을 하는 행사 안내문 철문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fff1359a-648b-490c-911e-3a12a57fc6b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3496b74d-8865-4f2c-81ba-97eabfd2719a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">차량 이동 등에 홍보용 부착</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0e1be5d-8525-4721-ac09-019d30ab7055\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c61dbb66-8530-4c0d-858e-d686396c9027\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-29fc38da-e85d-4283-8a53-06ab980caaaf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bb5d1851-c516-4eed-bce4-f553fc86f7c1\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>포맥스 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b570dae4-817d-46d4-ba12-aaef84eac01d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5744ea4-0695-46ec-bfb7-8e2938d97c4d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-66cccb01-09a8-45c3-ba19-c9991b39ce58\" style=\"color:#555555;\">외부 유리문에 큐방으로 접착이 가능한 지질</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2227aa9e-93db-4c2d-a626-6586768df780\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-82e3ffdc-8910-4f48-9851-a6078758c400\" style=\"color:#555555;\">영구적이 아닌 임시 큐방 부착물이 필요할 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37d8acb6-4605-4c67-86b8-63062c7d2d6a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f5031acc-1bd0-449a-b04d-d2a417bdfc26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">큐방 없이 외부 푯말이나 안내표지판 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebc85b42-6dc5-4013-9a7b-5811becccbb7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-30d8224c-0183-4b41-8c65-6dcff6ff1fd1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a86b88f7-4fbd-4ce7-9c3f-f0af15035b44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-82973109-a6db-4098-b48a-afdb71597e62\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>수량은 1개 부터 제작이 가능하며 가장 저렴하게 홍보할 수 있는 제품입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223784415941#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
